/**
 * Full leave-register **monthly pool carry** repair for one employee, a division, or everyone:
 * 1. **Strip (clean slate)** — delete all monthly pool carry rows: `MONTHLY_POOL_TRANSFER_OUT_*` / `IN_*`, plus legacy
 *    auto-generated carry rows that match the same “Transfer in/out — unused monthly apply pool …” reasons when
 *    `autoGeneratedType` was missing (so duplicates are actually removed before replay).
 *    clear carry metadata (including `poolCarryForwardAllocation`), and **subtract** prior carry-in from slot
 *    `clCredits` / `compensatoryOffs` / `elCredits` so counts are back to **native credits only** (no double carry-in).
 * 2. **Replay oldest → newest** — for each **closed** payroll month before the open cycle (sorted by `payPeriodEnd`),
 *    recompute unused pool from **credits − used − CL monthly-apply lock** (`monthlyApplyLocked`; legacy `lockedCredits` ignored), then **create** fresh transfer OUT on the
 *    closing slot and transfer IN on the next via `monthlyPoolCarryForwardService` (same as accrual cron).
 * 3. Caps replay to the **present payroll cycle month/year** by default (`--throughPresent true`) so June–Dec
 *    are not processed while you are still in May (same idea as production reconcile).
 * 4. Re-chains CL/CCL/EL ledger balances, syncs monthly apply + register display snapshot.
 * 5. Prints a per-month audit: register **Carried in / Transfer out** (view vs txn sums) plus **OK/MISMATCH**,
 *    and checks **Balance** = Credits + Carried in − Used − Transfer out vs API `poolBalance` when present.
 *
 * Usage (from backend folder):
 *   node scripts/reconcile_leave_register_pool_transactions.js --empNo 2146
 *   node scripts/reconcile_leave_register_pool_transactions.js --empNo 2146 --fy 2026
 *   node scripts/reconcile_leave_register_pool_transactions.js --all --limit 50
 *   node scripts/reconcile_leave_register_pool_transactions.js --divisionName "PYDAHSOFT"
 *
 * Flags:
 *   --asOf ISO              Reference “today” for open-cycle cutoff (default: now)
 *   --throughPresent false  Do not cap by current payroll cycle month/year (replay all closed months in FY)
 *   --throughPayrollMonth N Override month cap (e.g. 5)
 *   --throughPayrollYear Y  Override year (optional with month)
 *   --fy NAME               Financial year for audit table (default: FY for --asOf)
 *   --auditOnly true        Skip strip/replay; only print audit (read-only)
 *   --dryRun true           Print planned closing count + audit-only, no writes
 *   --clearPendingLocks false  Skip Phase 0 (default: run Phase 0 on full reconcile — reject
 *                              in-pipeline cap-counted leaves in pay periods with lock, sync apply fields, zero all slot `lockedCredits` for the employee)
 *
 * Env: MONGODB_URI or MONGO_URI
 */

